twitterfu: Automated twitter follow and unfollow

( Using latest version of twitcurl by the time of this
push; seems there's a problem while requesting oauth token in
method twitcurl::oAuthRequestToken() submitted the bug to the
author )

Deps
====

- boost
- twitcurl (http://code.google.com/p/twitcurl/)
- sqlite3

Compile
=======

./autogen.sh && ./configure && make && make install

Configure
=========

Type twitterfu, when you run the application for the first time you will be ask to enter
your password and username then a link to authorize the application using a PIN.

Database is a sqlite3 at $HOME/.twitterfu.sql
